{"tid":871464,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"摩連奴愛捉鬼","createTime":"2018-10-22T03:05:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T05:46:13.000Z","uid":7940,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"06c2312504590d693e5c57a3925ee80db0522520","tid":871464,"uid":7940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T03:05:54.000Z","msg":"曼聯喺英超作客以2:2打和車路士後，英國《鏡報》提到，紅魔嘅正選陣容喺比賽當日，即係英國時間星期六朝早喺網上流出，報道仲話，變陣內容只有教練組成員同球員知道，搞到領隊莫連奴扯晒火話要捉內鬼。 <br />\n<br />\n上個月曼聯喺聯賽作客以1:3不敵韋斯咸，正選陣容已經試過提前曝光，點知曼聯造訪史丹福橋球場，又再出現正選名單外洩事件，而且球迷應該知道，今次莫連奴用咗好多心思變陣，包括安排桑馬達打正選，咁搞法佢唔嬲就奇啦！<br />\n <a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20181022/mobile/bkn-20181022093958414-1022_00882_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20181022%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20181022093958414-1022_00882_001.html&d=%2B2ToEs93tEd13KwEjqwzmzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=a38421aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20181022/mobile/bkn-20181022093958414-1022_00882_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"065f2399f3c6fa0cec7a31919202283bdfbc3d75","tid":871464,"uid":7940,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T03:33:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/512586458998128642/0xtOwjRH_400x400.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fprofile_images%2F512586458998128642%2F0xtOwjRH_400x400.jpeg&h=4258cfa5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"940ac293d4a9e3303dbf1b2b0fbbf9b6f046ae7d","tid":871464,"uid":57035,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T03:54:06.000Z","msg":"咁大隻黑鬼都捉唔到<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.images.dailystar.co.uk/dynamic/58/photos/105000/620x/Paul-Pogba-Romelu-Lukaku-635605.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.images.dailystar.co.uk%2Fdynamic%2F58%2Fphotos%2F105000%2F620x%2FPaul-Pogba-Romelu-Lukaku-635605.jpg&h=3c300bcc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3678bb936823e1062da231f9f1941c2bcd84103c","tid":871